WorkItem.Description:
I am wanting to use the newly introduced method getDefaultColumnDimension() to set the default column width, but for some reason the width is not being picked up on the first column when using Excel2007 writer? Please check attachment.
 
Code snippet:
$PHPExcel = new PHPExcel();
$ws = $PHPExcel->getActiveSheet();
$ws->getDefaultColumnDimension()->setWidth(2);
$writer = new PHPExcel_Writer_Excel2007($PHPExcel);
$writer->save('defcol.xlsx');
 
